    "description": "<p>   <strong>WONG TAN & MOLLY LIM LLC (WTL) </strong>was established by a group of lawyers who, up to December 1986, were senior associates with the major international law firm Freshfields.  WTL is a limited liability law corporation.  We offer a comprehensive range of legal services to clients with international and local business interests.  Our firm focuses primarily on banking and finance, mergers and acquisitions, corporate finance, general corporate and commercial law, on-shore representation for foreign corporations, corporate and commercial litigation, arbitration, mediation and oher forms of dispute resolution.</p>  <p>    </p>  <p>    </p>  ",
